timing_disable...e_disable_arcs(25.10)  timing_disable...e_disable_arcs(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_tristate_disable_arcs

Syntax
       timing_disable_tristate_disable_arcs

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       When set to true, disables all 0/1->Z transitions of tristate arcs dur-
       ing timing analysis. By default, all tristate arcs are enabled.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

